<meta property="og:description" content="Infused with skin-loving ceramides and peptides, this nourishing lip balm locks in hydration and blurs for a fuller, plump look. Glides on smooth with a soft, cushiony feel and glossy finish.The cap features a built-in ring for charms and easily attaches to your keys, lanyard, or bag, so you’ll never lose another lip balm! Designed for sensitive lips without flavor, fragrance, or common irritants."><meta property="og:image" content="https://web.archive.org/web/20250501155815im_/http://www.cocokind.com/cdn/shop/files/Be_Kind.png?v=1744053875">
