										<p dir="ltr"><meta charset="utf-8"><meta charset="utf-8"><strong>As seen on TODAY! </strong>Infused with skin-loving ceramides and peptides, this nourishing lip balm locks in hydration and blurs for a fuller, plump look. Glides on smooth with a soft, cushiony feel and glossy finish. Buy 5 lip balms and get them for $50 ($60 value)! </p>
