    <span class="block w-full sm:w-fit text-p sm:text-p-bold !leading-relaxed text-secondary text-center pr-5 pl-7 sm:pl-2 !font-black lowercase"><strong>How do peptides and ceramides work together in this balm?</strong></span>
  </h2>
  <div data-hc-content="6-accordionCollapseOne2" class="!max-h-0 invisible" data-parent="#accordionFaqs">
    <div class="px-4 sm:px-16 lg:px-36 pb-4 text-center text-p !leading-1.2 group [&amp;_a]:text-orange [&amp;_a]:underline">
      <p><span style="font-size:10pt; font-variant:normal; white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-weight:400"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="text-decoration:none">Peptides help support your skin's natural repair processes and promote a plump, healthy look. Ceramides reinforce the skin barrier, locking in moisture and protecting your lips from environmental stressors. This lip balm deeply hydrates, smooths, and helps improve the appearance of your lips with the nourishing power of peptides and ceramides.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
